Required packages:

Qt4 development files
PyQt + PyOpenGL

In Ubuntu (and possibly in other Debian derivatives):
sudo apt-get install python-qt4 python-qt4-gl python-opengl

Syntax for running the program:
python CavityViewer.py examples/h2o.quad


Controls:

Left mouse button - rotate
Right mouse button - translate
Middle mouse button - zoom
Mouse wheel - zoom
